AURORA is a multi-edition you can claim via Manifold at no cost (only gas fee). This multi-series of surreal AI paintings were created using multiple AI software and a technique where Godwits applies a layering of abstract shapes as a signature to their work to represent figurative abstraction. Each work will have unique properties and each series will be rarer than the previous.
